<tr><td>Time to start producing</td><td>1–3 weeks</td><td>2–4 weeks</td></tr>
<tr><td>Monthly cost</td><td>$20–$2,000</td><td>$8K–$25K</td></tr>
<tr><td>Best for</td><td>Execution leverage on a defined strategy</td><td>Strategy + leadership for $5M–$50M ARR</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section>

